room_title: Escape room "Professor Death" by Escape Game Coeur d'Alene in Coeur d'Alene
room_description:
The famed criminal detective, Sherlock Holmes, and his crew are hot on the trail of the sinister Professor Death who has been on a global crime spree. Having tracked her to the university where she is posing as an instructor, Holmes and crew confront her.
However, something goes horribly wrong and they find themselves trapped. Can they break into her secret lair, find her next target and escape her evil clutches before the poisonous gas puts an end to our heroes? A tense 60 minutes is all they have!
